      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-060 Identify Impacts on Existing Suppliers
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3B8C0EBC-B9F1-4874-A386-872E34243733" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description-
Assess and Identify impacts of supplier standards on existing supply base. Review capabilities of suppliers regarding:
1. Pricing Scale and effective period 
2. Material/Service quality standards
3. Material/ Service availability
4. Delivery timeliness
5. Acceptable variance on quantities received
6. Use of Supplier's 'quantity shipped' in lieu of company-generated information
7. Labeling
8. Advance shipment notification
9. ISO 9000 certification
10. Adherence to ethical practices.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-46783355-517E-4F60-9AED-3F066F9967C3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Doc Locator specification:
*Supplier Selection Process Specification  (DL-0002375.pdf)
*Request for Question (RFQ) Governing Specification (DL-0002370.pdf)
 </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-94E095DB-A8ED-4237-AE61-128B62A3C38E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
